pullrequest.title: Compile and run fixes for OSX

content.raw:
The pull request looks good. I'd like to try to build it before approving it, but it looks like your fork of gazebo is private. Are you comfortable with making it public?

Since it's not going into default, I can test after merging, but I prefer to test first when possible.
